lead_paragraph: Holders Juventus swept aside old rivals Inter Milan 3-0 with some flowing attacking football and a brace from Alvaro Morata in the first leg of their Coppa Italia semi-final on Wednesday.

headline.print_headline: Rampant Juventus Sweep Aside Inter With Morata Brace
